data.description: Discover the epitome of suburban charm in this exquisite brick ranch home, now available in the heart of Virginia Beach. Just two streets away from the enchanting Lake Edwards, this residence offers a perfect blend of serenity and convenience. Nestled minutes from the bustling Little Creek Naval Base, Norfolk Premium Outlets, and the iconic IKEA, it seamlessly combines tranquility with urban accessibility. Inside, the home features sparkling stainless steel appliances and elegant granite countertops, adding a touch of modern sophistication. The spacious backyard is a hidden gem, providing an ideal setting for entertaining guests or simply enjoying the outdoors. Don't miss the chance to call this Virginia Beach haven your home!
